keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.

map g0 lastTab
map g1 firstTab
map g, previousTab
map , previousTab
map g. nextTab
map . nextTab
map <a-,> moveTabLeft
map <a-.> moveTabRight
map gb scrollToBottom
map gB Vomnibar.activateBookmarks
map D scrollDown
map U scrollUp
map gf LinkHints.activateMode

unmap f
unmap x
unmap X
unmap <a-m>
unmap <a-p>
unmap yt
unmap g$
unmap gt
unmap gT
unmap t
unmap H
unmap L
unmap ge
unmap gE
unmap b
unmap o
unmap O
unmap `
unmap m
unmap [[
unmap ]]
unmap <<
unmap >>
unmap gF
unmap v
unmap V
unmap i
unmap p
unmap P
unmap r
unmap h
unmap j
unmap J
unmap k
unmap K
unmap l
unmap <c-e>
unmap <c-y>
unmap /
